childNodes.textContent: Adam Sorensen was our realtor and did an awesome job taking care of our house hunting needs. He worked with us from day one to make sure we got the house of dreams. Since we were out of state buyers, Adam was our eyes and ears on site when we were unable to travel. He even made videos of the house we were having built so that we could see the progress. In addition, he sent us house updates daily and if a house jumped out at him, he would call and make sure we saw it. His personal touch made our experience memorable and I would recommend him to all my friends who are looking to purchase a home in Las Vegas. Adam is not just our realtor but we consider him a friend. He is awesome and we continue to lean on him after closing for ideas. He is even picking up the keys for or new house we just closed on since we had to fly back to Georgia before we could get them.

Hot City Homes went above and beyond what we asked for, particularly our realtor Adam Sorensen. Initially, we were looking for a house to buy, however, house after house didn't have everything we wanted. Our realtor helped us with the decision to buy land, and build our dream home. Several weeks later, we bought a half acre of land in the neighborhood we love, and look forward to building our home. Thank you!
- Pete S

Adam is fantastic. My sister and I wanted to move to Las Vegas. Adam spent many hours showing us all residential areas Las Vegas has to offer until we found the area that suited our needs. He very quickly determined what our absolute needs in a house and neighborhood were. Unfortunately we were not successful and need to return to our old home. Adam did not give up on us. He continued to view properties for us. He found the right one. He took us on a virtual tour of the house and the neighborhood. He helped us evaluate what a fair offer would be and we got the home. We are now in the home and settling in   
If you want a real estate professional that is knowledgeable and works hard for his clients Adam is your person. Thanks Adam!!!!
